AIXz_2y_DoQ7kNvgF9Q9jW&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCJNrqGgpOqGkW16w4DNpe9a3azRCoeqKaR4Zil43b1RA&oe=67484417"}, {"file_name": "level-select.png", "id": "861445076021181", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031640_861445079354514_4968430877850706782_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1rvaVE-6BtQQ7kNvgE3Di8K&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCuWxpz1dO8ZqeAvIWaix7xGGGR9UeBsLGcgtARVPHLfg&oe=67485372"}, {"file_name": "screenshot-5.png", "id": "1923238414795379", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984442_1923238418128712_4769228846090391027_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=apyuqqZ7qEgQ7kNvgGZT86C&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAxQVbTO2kvQnAWzBRRxoY69ivlKi4VzFZayqcziIVv-A&oe=67486A05"}, {"file_name": "equipment-terminal.png", "id": "3958226264503543", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75203624_3958226267836876_1387244605674504322_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=I8z4Q2ZxYn0Q7kNvgHc4Pk6&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDnqOudAtuIdza3XVGndQygR0tOwle5Q7zGzlG5jXVWwQ&oe=67487359"}, {"file_name": "screenshot-4_v2.png", "id": "1050360773266784", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031417_1050360776600117_7915853884089917557_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zuibeIeuIqkQ7kNvgFc0npj&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBGT5oicGB-fJyIHe2ce_vSm9EdW5xaeYG8Hp_Dr72qsQ&oe=6748673F"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "1191951792116232", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982570_1191951798782898_1277406797779782208_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=olmkFfTjED4Q7kNvgHvqTsW&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBe8e8SGlV6cJFnqI_pY3niktBtCWuOImQSLJG2bvcOGw&oe=6748739C"}, "display_name": "Shotwood Demo", "keywords": ["Shot", "Wood", "ShootWood", "Demo", "Free"], "long_description": "FREE vertical slice demo of Shotwood. Smash deadly wooden targets with realistic firearms & explosives while you try to escape from this ominous, ridiculous, mysterious facility. Shotwood is the casual (yet satisfyingly tactical) shoot-house themed game!\n\n{866219128900813}\n\n# Demo Features\n\nCheck out the awesome Shotwood gunplay with immediate access to some high end weaponry, plus the full practice range and 2 **shoot-house assessments**. Chill out in the home environment. Earn credits by completing runs and challenges, hunting the hidden cash wads, or mastering the ridiculous **Balloon Stabber** minigame. Spend credits on ammo, grenades, and gear - including the awesome **sidearm camera**. Find all the hidden clues to access a **secret demo area**!\n\n{427997739692963}\n\n# Full Game Features\n\nThe full Shotwood experience (not in demo) includes 8 shoot-house assessments with 15 challenges each and 3 modes, 20+ firearms, 9 tactical tools including **kamikaze drones** and the augmented visor, 2 minigame floors, playable arcade cabinet, facility induction process, **progression system**, working grievance booth, big secret area \"beyond the booth\", more **story** to uncover including 120 random announcements, 4 save slots, various difficulty options including **permadeath**, new game plus, and even more!\n\n{2300077013672023}\n\n# Tech Features\n\nShotwood runs at a **smooth 90hz refresh rate**, supports full room scale movement as well as seated play, and offers multiple options for movement, haptics, captions, and whole lot more.\n\nGrab this **FREE** demo right now and... SHOOT SOME WOOD!", "short_description": "FREE vertical slice demo of Shotwood. Smash deadly wooden targets with realistic firearms & explosives while you try to escape from this ominous, ridiculous, mysterious facility. Shotwood is the casual (yet satisfyingly tactical) shoot-house themed game!"}]}, "developer_name": n